{"name":"Animated Cauldron","size":"medium","type":"construct","tag":"","alignment":"neutral","hitDice":"10","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":4,"otherArmorDesc":"12 (magical ward)","speed":"0","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"50 (damage threshold 15)","speedDesc":"15 ft.","strPoints":"12","dexPoints":"4","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"1","wisPoints":"1","chaPoints":"1","blindsight":"60","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"2 (450 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"","isLair":true,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the [MON] can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the [MON] can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"Each of these lair actions may only happen once over the course of combat.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the mimic's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the mimic's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the mimic dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[],"actions":[{"name":"Animate Items","desc":"The [MON] animates [2d4] objects from the surroundings. The objects have initiative count 10.\n\nAnimated Object Statistics\n- Tiny   1HP, AC 18, +3 to hit, [1d4] Str: 4, Dex: 18\n- Small  10HP, AC 16, +3 to hit, [1d8] Str: 6, Dex: 14\n- Medium: 15HP, AC 13, +2 to hit, [2d6] Str: 10, Dex: 12\n\nRoll 1d6, on a 1-2 this includes the _Vorpal Cleaver_ ([2d4+1], +4 to hit).\n\nTotal items: Medium: 5, Small: 30, Tiny: 100"}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[{"name":"Steam Burst","desc":"A nearby pipe or vent releases a sudden jet of scalding steam. Creatures in a 10-ft line must make a DC 12 dexterity save or take [2d8] fire damage. The air fills with the smell of rosemary and burnt copper."},{"name":"The Angry Ladle","desc":"A tarnished silver ladle suddenly snaps upright and begins smacking anything nearby. It flails in a 5-foot radius causing all creatures to make a DC 10 dexterity save or else they take [1d12] bludgeoning damage. The handle continues to twitch for a minute afterward, like it’s scolding you."},{"name":"Phantom Wait Staff","desc":"Faint outlines of _Unseen Servant_ manifest briefly, attempting to tabletop several creatures. Three creatures within 60ft must make a DC 12 Dexterity saving through or be knocked prone."},{"name":"The Soufflé’s Revenge","desc":"From beneath a collapsed prep table oozes a blob of half-animated dough--the ghost of an unfinished meal. It jiggles weakly toward the nearest creature, bumping them before evaporating into a cloud of spores. Each creature within 20ft must make a DC 10 constitution save or be poisoned for 1 minute."}],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"fire","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"lightning","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"necrotic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"poison","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"psychic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"blinded"},{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"deafened"},{"name":"exhaustion"},{"name":"frightened"},{"name":"incapacitated"},{"name":"paralyzed"},{"name":"poisoned"},{"name":"prone"},{"name":"restrained"},{"name":"stunned"},{"name":"unconscious"}],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"cauldron","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}